{"tid":1458933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"致計劃8月13至16日塞鐵巴絲們一番說話","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T00:30:13.000Z","uid":127451,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6a440f2ccc4b12b94081f82cca1c4903513f51","tid":1458933,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"我知道大家對8月12號爆眼少女一事覺得好氣憤，亦對港鐵好憤怒，但唔好被憤怒支配。<br />\n呢一場運動，最成功係不分化不分割，不論和理非定勇武都係連為一體，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即使意見不同，由集體決定，少數服從多數</span></span>，先係堅持到現在既原因。<br />\n既然之前做過投票，有61%人反對，為何要堅持己見？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅持己見，一意孤行，請問，你同777有咩分別？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好活在自己世界，唔好以為眾人皆醉唯你獨醒，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請Be Humble.</span></span>"},{"pid":"eea1d683edbc5d001559471bb620f6768c55dfde","tid":1458933,"uid":187510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"塞鐵必須配合罷工 亂塞只會得不償失"},{"pid":"a2ec34406e10143d93ed5193a9e160491ba0de3f","tid":1458933,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"55aad47a3d8e6fe164b3b5e85bd1e83dc953ca1e","tid":1458933,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:35:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b999548e4517d6cb5bd8f0df94bf90d1edc76a7b","tid":1458933,"uid":186836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f916b2668de6d24215e12472cafa0fa8b2c098c8","tid":1458933,"uid":35422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"有勇更要有謀<br />\n811輿論又轉向，全城圍插<br />\n就趁依個時間做多啲文宣<br />\n好多港豬廢